{"tid":872863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加國大麻遭搶購 大麻股 ETF 大瀉","createTime":"2018-10-23T04:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T04:34:07.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bddf6386085c3685bb98ee6e7cc903bec02194ed","tid":872863,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T04:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181023/large/1540252893_3d02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181023%2Flarge%2F1540252893_3d02.jpg&h=84b4f09e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加拿大大麻合法後，僅僅4日即遭狂購，零售商存貨沽清。於美上市的大麻反大瀉，Tilray收跌15.6%，報122.6美元；大麻ETF ETFMG Alternative Harvest ETF (MJ)亦跌近一成，於加拿大上市的Horizons Marijuana Life Sciences ETF亦曾跌14%。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大總理杜魯道（Justin Trudeau）日前宣佈大麻合化法，成烏拉圭後全球第2個全面大麻合法化的國家。根據新例，每戶可種4棵大麻（曼尼托巴及魁北克省則禁種），成人出外可帶不多於30克大麻自用。據悉加拿大有490萬大麻吸食者。"},{"pid":"1c940e9892773b3ffd8e796a4c8eb33821b6d293","tid":872863,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T04:34:07.000Z","msg":"原來大麻有ETF <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}